thread.title: Canada's parliament sings new gender-neutral national anthem

title: Canada's parliament sings new gender-neutral national anthem
text:
Canada's parliament sings new gender-neutral national anthem Thursday, February 08, 2018 - 01:08 
Canadian members of parliament sang the new, gender-neutral lyrics to their national anthem on Wednesday just hours after the change was officially enshrined in law. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
